data.description: Don't miss your chance with this charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home. Located in the desirable Cedar Park Subdivision! Ranch-style home with a beautiful sunroom and private backyard for year around entertainment. Conveniently located near I64, Shopping Centers, Langley Air Force Base, Hampton University and Christopher Newport Univ & Fort Eustis are just a short commute away. This well kept home is move-in ready, making it an excellent opportunity for first-time buyers or those seeking a downsize and lighten their load! HURRY, make this house your next home!
